itunes:title: 36 We Mature From Archetype to Archetype
title: 36 We Mature From Archetype to Archetype
description:
Do we grow and mature in a smooth, straight line? I don't think so. Jungian psychology says we mature in stages that correspond to the archetypes of the Unconscious--Youth to Warrior to Mentor to Father to King (or Queen) to Sage to Mystic. We'll examine this in today's episode.

New episodes every Monday. SUBSCRIBE and REVIEW.
